    "proxy_gap": "\"Leftist\" and \"queer\" are both inferred, not measured. SAME_SEX = 1\n(heavy soft) catches partnered queer records; the lifestyle bundle\n(creative or social-service occupation, no-car-urban-renter, part-time-\nbonused, DREM, nonfamily household, college enrolment) catches single\nLGBTQ records and lifestyle-aligned leftist allies. Cultural performance,\npolitics, and religion are not capturable in PUMS. The DREM weight\nencodes the LGBTQ minority-stress correlation (Meyer 2003) but is\nbroader than psychiatric diagnosis. The CA non-white-identity weight\nis the single documented exception to the no-race-gating principle\n(see METHODOLOGY)."
  },
