    "proxy_gap": "Aimed at the severe-untreated-mental-illness archetype. DREM (cognitive\n/ mental-health difficulty) is the heaviest soft signal at weight 5;\nthe structural gate is DIS=1 + PUBCOV=1 + age 25-55. The \"stinks like\npiss\" detail is proxied by PLM=2 (incomplete plumbing \u2014 no shower /\nno toilet); the unhoused / sheltered subset is captured by RELSHIPP=38\n(noninstitutionalized group quarters) and TEN=4 (occupied without\npayment). PUMS does not reach the entirely unsheltered population.\nAddiction, psychiatric diagnosis, criminal-justice involvement, and\nyelling-in-public are unmeasurable. Geography expected: Tenderloin and\nMission (SF), Skid Row and parts of Hollywood (LA), East Oakland,\ncentral San Diego, downtown Sacramento, plus the working-class non-\nmajor cities (Stockton, Modesto, Bakersfield, Fresno, San Bernardino)."
